Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.88,0:00:11.59,Luna,,0,0,0,,Greetings, Tantabus. I am ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.59,0:00:13.45,Luna,,0,0,0,,Do your worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.92,0:00:22.19,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Princess Luna is turning into Nightmare Moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.19,0:00:23.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.15,0:00:32.67,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, we've got the cure for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:53.68,Luna,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:00:55.68,Luna,,0,0,0,,What is it doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:00:57.98,Luna,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.98,0:00:59.37,Luna,,0,0,0,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.91,0:01:09.99,Luna,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.99,0:01:12.51,Luna,,0,0,0,,My dream ended… happily?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.65,0:01:15.34,Luna,,0,0,0,,That cannot happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.37,0:01:54.96,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.48,0:02:00.10,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Rarity. Thanks for setting all this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.10,0:02:03.45,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,A grooming day for our pets really was a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.39,0:02:11.73,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Ooh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:13.15,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:16.58,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I didn't get my normal beauty sleep last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.51,0:02:18.36,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You know…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.60,0:02:21.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I didn't sleep well either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.71,0:02:26.20,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I'm totally beat, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.43,0:02:30.54,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,All right, Winona. Time for your brushing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:41.22,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm too plum-tuckered out to do this right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:45.42,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I even went to bed early last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:48.35,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,But then I had a really scary nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:50.31,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:51.54,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Uh, only, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:53.61,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I didn't think mine was that scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:54.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, mine sure was.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.95,0:02:57.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There was this blue smoke monster, and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.39,0:03:00.19,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:03.20,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I dreamt about a blue smoke thingy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:04.66,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:05.91,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:07.74,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Probably just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.74,0:03:10.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That's an awfully big coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:12.83,Spike,,0,0,0,,Huh, I wonder why I didn't have that nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:14.79,Spike,,0,0,0,,I slept great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:20.26,Rarity,,0,0,0,,So, then, what could have given us all the same nightmare?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:21.51,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:23.01,Twilight,,0,0,0,,but I do know who might.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:25.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Spike, could you send a scroll to Princess Luna?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:27.21,Spike,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.76,0:03:28.78,Spike,,0,0,0,,All set.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.78,0:03:30.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,"Dear Princess Luna,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.53,0:03:32.58,Twilight,,0,0,0,,last night, my friends and I all dreamt
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:35.37,Twilight,,0,0,0,,of a creature made of blue smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.37,0:03:37.84,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you're very busy, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:40.77,Twilight,,0,0,0,,When you have the chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:43.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,please let me know if you have any idea what it could mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:45.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:48.21,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight Sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.21,0:03:50.21,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You can leave out the yawns.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.16,0:04:00.26,Luna,,0,0,0,,Which of you saw the creature of blue smoke in your nightmare?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:02.55,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Wow. That was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:03.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We all did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:05.83,Spike,,0,0,0,,Not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.83,0:04:07.43,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Ugh, we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:10.45,Twilight,,0,0,0,,So, you've encountered the smoke monster, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:13.02,Luna,,0,0,0,,The Tantabus is a creature of my nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:15.59,Luna,,0,0,0,,It escaped from my slumbers yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:18.61,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,But how did it get into ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:20.69,Luna,,0,0,0,,The Tantabus is like a parasite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:23.24,Luna,,0,0,0,,My dreams must no longer be enough for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:25.90,Luna,,0,0,0,,Now it seeks others to infect and corrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:29.05,Luna,,0,0,0,,He must have learned of you six from seeing you in my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:32.14,Spike,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa, whoa. So what you're saying is,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:35.31,Spike,,0,0,0,,you dreamt about all of them and not me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:39.62,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Uh, so, smokey gave us bad dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:40.75,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,No biggie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:44.31,Luna,,0,0,0,,I saw that the Tantabus had grown more powerful,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:49.01,Luna,,0,0,0,,but I did not realize that power was enough to enable it to escape my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:50.63,Luna,,0,0,0,,If its power grows,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.63,0:04:54.21,Luna,,0,0,0,,it could very well find a way to escape into the real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:57.86,Luna,,0,0,0,,It could turn all of Equestria into a living nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:02.74,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, okay. I take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:04.25,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That does sound bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.25,0:05:06.25,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.15,0:05:12.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We've prepared everything exactly as you requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:17.12,Luna,,0,0,0,,Good. As you six slumber here, I will pursue the creature into
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:19.16,Luna,,0,0,0,,whichever of your dreams it infests.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:22.65,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Ooh! It'll be like a princess sleepover!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:24.30,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Speaking of princesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:27.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,aren't you gonna ask Celestia for her help, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:29.29,Luna,,0,0,0,,There is nothing my sister can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.29,0:05:31.78,Luna,,0,0,0,,She has no power in the realm of sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:34.01,Luna,,0,0,0,,Only I can move from dream to dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:36.65,Luna,,0,0,0,,I am afraid nopony can help me tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.65,0:05:37.99,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Even us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:39.29,Luna,,0,0,0,,Especially you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:42.28,Luna,,0,0,0,,You have all suffered so much because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:46.15,Luna,,0,0,0,,You need only slumber while I hunt the Tantabus in your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.41,0:05:51.04,Spike,,0,0,0,,I know you said nopony can help, but I'm no pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.04,0:05:54.51,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna stay up and watch over you guys, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:57.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:01.17,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,One good thing about not sleeping well last night
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:03.55,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't be too hard to fall asleep now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:04.88,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:08.50,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,This is so exciting I don't know how I'm ever going to…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:44.59,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.94,0:06:47.01,Rarity,,0,0,0,,This is simply divine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:50.87,Rarity,,0,0,0,,How avant-garde!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:58.33,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Forget avant-garde!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:00.98,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I should have said en garde!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:06.73,Luna,,0,0,0,,It is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:16.71,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It was such a pretty little chiffon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.71,0:07:19.63,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What kind of monster would do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:20.92,Luna,,0,0,0,,The Tantabus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:22.53,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Then let's stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:23.29,Luna,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:24.26,Luna,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.26,0:07:27.20,Luna,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to suffer any more because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:29.22,Luna,,0,0,0,,I will catch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:40.93,Luna,,0,0,0,,It has jumped into another dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:44.61,Luna,,0,0,0,,I am sorry, but if I am to stop it, I must follow it where you cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:45.83,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:49.12,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I shall be able to handle things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.98,0:07:51.40,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:07:59.64,Luna,,0,0,0,,I followed the Tantabus here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:01.73,Luna,,0,0,0,,Now I need only find…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:05.69,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Sorry, can't help it. An idea pops into my head and…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:07.54,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Ooh, cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:17.52,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Ew, cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:27.96,Luna,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:29.54,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:34.28,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Who wants ice cream?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:41.13,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,It's so nice to be the pet for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:53.56,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,N-n-nice, giant, evil Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:09:00.05,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:13.49,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Now, this is what I call an incredible dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:43.00,Luna,,0,0,0,,I can see the Tantabus has already turned your slumbers into a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:44.86,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.86,0:09:46.77,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,This is my favorite dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:56.18,Somepony,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are such happy flowers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:10:00.61,Somepony,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We will now sing for hours.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:04.49,Somepony,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aren't we unbearably cute?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:09.77,Somepony,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Watch me solo on this flute!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:39.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:52.56,Spike,,0,0,0,,What happened? Are you guys okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:55.03,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,That… that was terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:58.73,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I-I never want to have that nightmare again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:01.26,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Me either!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:04.09,Spike,,0,0,0,,But Luna caught it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.09,0:11:05.03,Spike,,0,0,0,,didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:07.08,Luna,,0,0,0,,I am so sorry, my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:08.52,Luna,,0,0,0,,I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.09,0:11:12.98,Luna,,0,0,0,,It will be back to infect your dreams the next time you sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:14.40,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:19.82,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I reckon I could live without seeing that thing ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:21.03,Luna,,0,0,0,,But you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:23.13,Luna,,0,0,0,,Again and again. Every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:26.65,Luna,,0,0,0,,Until it grows powerful enough to infect the waking world!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.65,0:11:28.98,Luna,,0,0,0,,After what I did as Nightmare Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:33.80,Luna,,0,0,0,,the fact that I am once again responsible for harming others is more than I can bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:35.26,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:37.37,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Everypony makes mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.37,0:11:39.92,Luna,,0,0,0,,As long as none of you dreamt about another pony
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:42.42,Luna,,0,0,0,,the Tantabus remains confined to your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.42,0:11:45.19,Luna,,0,0,0,,I still have a chance to catch it before it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.82,0:11:47.30,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,That's good to hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:48.86,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Although after you left, I did happen to dream
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.86,0:11:50.93,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,that I was eating a giant ice cream cone with all of Ponyville
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:52.66,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,while taking a test we hadn't studied for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.66,0:11:54.30,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,See? What I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:56.72,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Everypony makes mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:06.77,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But that means the Tantabus could be turning every dream in Ponyville into a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:08.21,Luna,,0,0,0,,It is far worse than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:11.50,Luna,,0,0,0,,Infecting all of those dreams gives it more and more power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:13.86,Luna,,0,0,0,,Soon, it will be able to escape into the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.86,0:12:16.44,Luna,,0,0,0,,and infect Equestria with its nightmare plague.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:19.62,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Then you must let us help you stop it before that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:20.81,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.81,0:12:22.64,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,The Tantabus was able to escape Luna
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:25.33,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,when it only had six dreams it could get to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.33,0:12:26.45,Luna,,0,0,0,,It is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:30.85,Luna,,0,0,0,,With so many dreams to hide in, I do not know how I can catch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.84,0:12:35.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What if every pony in ponyville were having one dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:39.53,Luna,,0,0,0,,I can create shared dreams, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:41.79,Luna,,0,0,0,,But for so many ponies at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.79,0:12:43.89,Luna,,0,0,0,,I have never done anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:46.11,Luna,,0,0,0,,The amount of power it would take…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:48.68,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Well, it is worth a try,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:49.70,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:50.63,Luna,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:52.42,Luna,,0,0,0,,I will do anything to end this,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.42,0:12:54.42,Luna,,0,0,0,,including accept your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:57.50,Luna,,0,0,0,,I cannot allow the Tantabus to escape into the real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:13:00.12,Luna,,0,0,0,,All of you must now go back to sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.12,0:13:03.50,Luna,,0,0,0,,and hope that I can create such a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.19,0:13:47.37,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Princess Luna did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:52.17,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Big Mac!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:55.31,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Boy, I'm glad to see something familiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:13:59.09,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Ee-yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:00.94,Luna,,0,0,0,,Ponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:03.94,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Princess Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:07.17,Luna,,0,0,0,,There is no time for bowing, my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:10.33,Luna,,0,0,0,,There is something coming, something terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.33,0:14:12.62,Luna,,0,0,0,,No, it is already here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:21.30,Luna,,0,0,0,,I am so sorry! I brought this upon you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.30,0:14:23.63,Luna,,0,0,0,,But I will end it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:32.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Princess, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:38.62,Luna,,0,0,0,,It is taking all my strength just to hold this massive dream together!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:40.35,Luna,,0,0,0,,You will have to stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:43.82,Luna,,0,0,0,,I truly wish I did not have to ask this of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.72,0:14:46.11,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Then you're in luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:48.07,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're already on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:07.28,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:09.97,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I'll pay you anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:15.18,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.14,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:38.91,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Big Mac,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:42.21,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You can do anything in a dream, remember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:01.42,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:04.73,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,If that Tantabus thing turns any more of this dream against us,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:07.41,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,we will to busy saving ponies to catch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:11.75,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And it will grow powerful enough to escape into the real world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:15.42,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,How are we even gonna know when it's able to escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:22.79,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oh, I think we'll know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:34.50,Luna,,0,0,0,,Hurry, my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:39.89,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What the?..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:43.86,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Please! We need your help, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:49.08,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy is right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:52.35,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We've all got to work together to stop it from escaping!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.35,0:16:53.69,MrCake,,0,0,0,,But how can we help?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.69,0:16:56.38,MrCake,,0,0,0,,Nopony in Ponyville has your magic
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:57.66,MrCake,,0,0,0,,or your speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:16:59.75,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:01.60,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,In Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:03.64,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,But this here isn't Ponyville,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:04.54,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,it's a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:08.69,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And not just any!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:10.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This is your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:12.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Anything you can do in your dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:13.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,you can do now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.08,0:17:20.06,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, if you're gonna dream, might as well dream big, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.11,0:18:00.30,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,It's working!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:02.47,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But it's not enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.79,0:18:08.20,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Then do more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:10.06,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,This is a dream, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.39,0:18:40.38,Luna,,0,0,0,,I cannot hold this dream together much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:42.30,Luna,,0,0,0,,Equestria will fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:43.86,Luna,,0,0,0,,Because of me…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.55,0:18:52.95,Spike,,0,0,0,,Am I crazy or
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:56.40,Spike,,0,0,0,,did it just get even bigger after Luna said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.33,0:19:00.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I think it's feeding of your guilt, Princess Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:01.72,Luna,,0,0,0,,If that is so,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:06.08,Luna,,0,0,0,,then perhaps that is how it grew strong enough to escape in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.92,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Say what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.93,0:19:12.08,Luna,,0,0,0,,I created the Tantabus
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:15.34,Luna,,0,0,0,,to give myself the same nightmare every night,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:19.97,Luna,,0,0,0,,to punish myself for the evil I caused as Nightmare Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:22.59,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,But why would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:25.52,Luna,,0,0,0,,To make sure I never forgave myself
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.52,0:19:28.42,Luna,,0,0,0,,for how much equestria suffered because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:30.69,Luna,,0,0,0,,But it seems I have not learned my lesson,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:34.01,Luna,,0,0,0,,for now I have only made you suffer more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:40.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But that means you might just be the key to stopping all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:40.98,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.98,0:19:45.38,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,If it gets strong because you feel bad about what you did as Nightmare Moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.38,0:19:48.94,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,then you've just got to stop feeling bad for what you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.94,0:19:50.62,Luna,,0,0,0,,How can I forgive myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:53.35,Luna,,0,0,0,,I am no better now than I was then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:58.40,Luna,,0,0,0,,My creation is about to turn the world into a living nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:20:00.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But look at what you're doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:04.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Nightmare moon would have wanted the Tantabus to turn Equestria into a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.83,0:20:07.39,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You're doing everything you can to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:08.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:11.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That proves you're not the same pony you were then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:15.27,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Everypony who knows you knows that Nightmare Moon is in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:17.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We all trust you, Luna.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:21.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Do you trust us enough to believe we're right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:26.53,Luna,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.21,0:20:44.60,Luna,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.60,0:20:46.54,Luna,,0,0,0,,Thank you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.61,0:20:55.36,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Luna did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:20:58.66,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,She sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.66,0:21:01.98,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Only, I'm not exactly sure what she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:04.74,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Luna created the tantabus to punish herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:07.63,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The worse she felt, the more power it had.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.63,0:21:11.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But once she finally forgave herself for what Nightmare Moon did…
